	<div class="cf-faq-header-text">Buy</div>
	<div class="cf-faq-answer">
	<p><b>Online Shopping Portals</b></p>
	<p>You have to follow the “Visit Shop” link which will lead you to respective shopping portal. From the portal, you can buy the product.</p>
	<p><b>Retailers near your locality</b></p>
	<p>Visit the retailers shop page in CrawlFish by following 'Visit Shop'. There you can find contact details and location of shop in map. You can choose to visit the shop in person or send SMS to that seller using our “SEND SMS” in retailers shop page or contact the retailer using contact details.</p>
	</div>
	<br/>
	<div class="cf-faq-header-text">CrawlFish Price Search</div>
	<div class="cf-faq-answer">
	<p>In CrawlFish, we offer an innovative way of searching for products across all categories. Say, you want to search for all those products that can be bought for Rs.1000. It is simple, indeed.</p>
	<ul>
	<li>Visit “Price Finder” from our home page.</li>
	<li>Key in Rs.1000.</li>
	<li>You will get all products that can be bought for Rs.1000.</li>
	<li>You can also refine your search by category and type of shops [online shopping portals or retailers near your locality]</li>
	</ul>
	</div>


